commentTextItems.html: pushed past the fielders in the offside to the cover boundary to bring up a crushing 9 wicket victory for Ireland

commentPostTextItems.html: So thanks to contributions from most of the Irish bolwers and the fireworks from the bat of Stirling Ireland are able to complete a 2-0 series whitewash over the Dutch.
Thanks for joining us for the two games and from Conor Hayes in Dublin it's goodbye.

milestones.description: Johnston has become the top wicket-taker for IRE in ODIs with 40 wickets, going past Kyle McCallan's 39
Bas Zuiderent has broken the record for most ducks (6) in ODIs for NED, going past Peter Borren's 5
This is the lowest match aggregate (254) involving teams Netherlands & Ireland in ODIs

stories.title: Ireland take series 2-0 after nine-wicket drubbing
stories.subTitle: Ireland v Netherlands, 2nd ODI, Dublin
stories.seoTitle: Ireland v Netherlands: Ireland take series 2-0 after nine-wicket drubbing
